## How to Run (Backend)

From the project root:

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r backend/requirements.txt
python -m uvicorn backend.app.main:app --reload
Then open:
http://127.0.0.1:8000
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs (API testing)

Notes
Letterboxd data is processed in memory and never stored
IMDb data is preprocessed once into a compact format for fast lookup
Generated data files can be safely deleted and rebuilt